Package: servr
Type: Package
Title: A simple HTTP server in R
Version: 0.1.4
Date: 2013-10-05
Author: Yihui Xie
Maintainer: Yihui Xie <xie@yihui.name>
Description: Start a simple HTTP server in R to serve static files or documents
    that can be converted to HTML files (e.g. R Markdown) under a given
    directory.
Imports:
    mime (>= 0.1.1),
    httpuv (>= 1.2.0)
License: GPL
URL: https://github.com/yihui/servr
BugReports: https://github.com/yihui/servr/issues
